    "name": "RAGDOLL UNIVERSE",
    "steam_appid": 3136560,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136560/extras/1a4de470d3b2888ef4e74fea9ae08719.avif?t=1735168380\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136560/extras_big/1a4de470d3b2888ef4e74fea9ae08719.avif?t=1735168380 width=800 height=264 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dive into a world of RAGDOLL characters with our unique and fun game! Get ready to take on challenges specially designed to let you enjoy the hilarious physics of characters fully affected by gravity and environmental forces. Shoot, fight, jump, push, and perform countless actions in this exciting challenge-based game.&quot;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136560/extras/79fe228717435965227a0d29418f7cd5.poster.avif?t=1735168380\" width=800 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136560/extras/79fe228717435965227a0d29418f7cd5.webm?t=1735168380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136560/extras/79fe228717435965227a0d29418f7cd5.mp4?t=1735168380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each challenge is inspired by popular games and famous situations, offering you a varied and entertaining experience. Your goal is to rack up as many &quot;ragdoll&quot; points as possible. With these points, you can unlock new characters and upgrades to enhance your experience in Sandbox mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136560/extras/f9827d32ec807b0750bb200f44c4e921.poster.avif?t=1735168380\" width=800 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136560/extras/f9827d32ec807b0750bb200f44c4e921.webm?t=1735168380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136560/extras/f9827d32ec807b0750bb200f44c4e921.mp4?t=1735168380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main Features (As of Update 0.43):</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&quot;Challenges&quot; mode</strong> with 10 challenges to overcome</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&quot;Sandbox&quot; mode</strong> with 1 open-world map to play solo or in local multiplayer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Option to play in <strong>split-screen</strong> or <strong>shared-screen</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>7 maps</strong> in &quot;Versus&quot; mode for local multiplayer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1 map</strong> in &quot;Challenges Coop&quot; mode for local multiplayer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>30 outfit and accessory variations</strong> to mix and match</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>7 rewards</strong> to unlock with &quot;Ragdoll Points&quot;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>7 structures</strong> to build in &quot;Sandbox&quot; mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ability to drive <strong>cars</strong>, <strong>helicopters</strong>, and <strong>planes</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Together Mode</strong> (Play online with friends in your local multiplayer sessions)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136560/extras/2269bbdffec61d31c816a446592c1932.poster.avif?t=1735168380\" width=800 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136560/extras/2269bbdffec61d31c816a446592c1932.webm?t=1735168380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136560/extras/2269bbdffec61d31c816a446592c1932.mp4?t=1735168380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our Discord to get all the latest updates, suggest new maps, or share any ideas you think would make the game even better.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136560/extras/1a18e921d6163c6f71da26e0ef937e4f.poster.avif?t=1735168380\" width=800 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136560/extras/1a18e921d6163c6f71da26e0ef937e4f.webm?t=1735168380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136560/extras/1a18e921d6163c6f71da26e0ef937e4f.mp4?t=1735168380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to laugh, challen ge yourself, and enjoy hours of entertainment? Join the fun and discover everything our physics-based &quot;ragdoll&quot; game has to offer!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136560/extras/3efc792e88866f072f4dce49ca449906.poster.avif?t=1735168380\" width=800 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136560/extras/3efc792e88866f072f4dce49ca449906.webm?t=1735168380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136560/extras/3efc792e88866f072f4dce49ca449906.mp4?t=1735168380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
